# Auto Rotate CID (Caller ID)

<Callout>
This feature is only available on Tonet hosted Vicidial systems.
</Callout>

With this integration the numbers you buy with Tonet will automatically be put into your campaigns Caller ID Rotation.

1. Go to your **Campaign Details View**. 
2. Scroll down to **CID Group** and select **TonetAutoRotate**
![Campaign_CID_Group](https://i.imgur.com/VnwIQaz.png)
3. All the numbers purchased or removed in the Tonet Dashboard will be reflected in this CID Group.

To check the available numbers go to **Admin - CID Groups** and click on **TonetAutoRotate**

![CID_Group_Numbers](https://i.imgur.com/1mbhFCr.png)

Do not make any manual changes to this group.